name: Lax.O1
description: Lax is the 2nd member of the Oxbot-X team. He is the smartest boy in the group. The Oxbot-X team was brought together from 3 gladiators who winning the arane battles in the great kingdom. 3 armors made by Merkars are given to this team. Lax uses silver armor. Their aim is to assassinate the ruthless Veroun.
